{"tid":1582243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"何妖： 明天清潔香港行動如期舉行","createTime":"2019-09-20T03:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T10:10:49.000Z","uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a89917dff14c1db5d08faf974f4ecf4ac25ab9e4","tid":1582243,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"佢話淨係唔使同克警申請不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f0f18bd22dcb2a0a4d426d3b6831e955d60eae","tid":1582243,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T10:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nqctagq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnqctagq.png&h=7fed4eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我朋友係福建人<br />\n<br />\n佢話何生琴日係街比馬迷鬧係過街老鼠<br />\n<br />\n新聞訪問阿叔又係咁鬧何生<br />\n<br />\n何生依家準備吹大雞要打馬迷 開始召集福建幫<br />\n<br />\n仲話呢排一見到有人拎馬經就話要打<br />\n<br />\n佢地今次唔係針對果班暴徒曱甴<br />\n<br />\n係針對我地班馬迷 各位黎緊跑馬既馬迷要小心！<br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安"}]}